: "今天跑步跑得特别狼狈。 在河边沿河跑道跑步经过一处快拆迁的房子时，遭到了此处一只田园犬的威胁。 丫老远朝我吠了。 我不以为然，以为它会原地不动，叫下而已。 然，老夫预判错了。 四条腿向我冲来，呲牙咧嘴低吼。 我大惊：遇到咬人的狗了？！ 马上停下来呵斥，丫没有被吓到。 胆子很大一只花斑狗。 此时一老太太慢悠悠「过来」。 「你的狗？」 「对！」她边过来边轰狗，然，这狗只是不叫了。 仍然在我身边徘徊。 「你戴了个帽子，它觉得…」 冬天跑步戴个帽子不是很正常啊。 就招惹它了？ 花狗被赶走… 我得以脱身。 下次看来要么换条路线，要么提前备好一棍子。 再碰到，揍它一顿。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-48861d6ad6cfbbacfcfd6c74dd5b43f3_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7486026500"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8P6C1czEx4dUEAMaCTExMjQ3MzgwOCC2kpu7BjAAOExAB3IKNzQ4NjAyNjUwMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1735118546.877616", "card_id": "Q_6684021762", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「情感勒索」是什么？有心理学依据吗？怎样分辨伴侣之间是普通的冲突，还是「情感勒索」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-25fda273049ca7effe5e34b0395d59eb_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6684021762"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8P6C1czEx4dUEAMaCTExMjMxMzQ5MyCVg+u6BjAAOFlACHIKNjY4NDAyMTc2MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1735118546.878148", "card_id": "Q_7718728238", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_spe